#: ../../docs/classes/class_quat.rst:17
msgid "A unit quaternion used for representing 3D rotations."
msgstr "用于表示3D旋转的单位四元数。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_quat.rst:19
msgid ""
"It is similar to :ref:`Basis <class_Basis>`, which implements matrix "
"representation of rotations, and can be parametrized using both an axis-"
"angle pair or Euler angles. But due to its compactness and the way it is "
"stored in memory, certain operations (obtaining axis-angle and performing"
" SLERP, in particular) are more efficient and robust against floating-"
"point errors."
msgstr ""
"它类似于 :ref:`Basis "
"<class_Basis>`，实现旋转的矩阵表示，并且使用一个轴角对或欧拉角，都可以进行参数化。但是由于其紧凑性和将其存储在内存中的方式，某些操作（尤其是获取轴角度并执行SLERP）对于浮点错误更有效且更可靠。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_quat.rst:21
msgid "Quaternions need to be (re)normalized."
msgstr "四元数需要（重新）归一化。"

